resources.string:
This application is intended only for persons that are authorized to access Fidelity Digital Assets accounts.

If you are a credentialed user, please click “OK” below to proceed to the log-in page.

If you are not a registered customer of Fidelity Digital Assets, please close and uninstall this application.
A WiFi or cellular network connection is required to use this application. Please check your network settings, then try again.

If you need assistance, contact our Client 
 Service Team:

 or
